1.
 Purpose
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
This policy governs the recovery of IT systems,
 services,
 and infrastructure following cybersecurity incident eradication,
 the 
\series bold
Operational Handback
\series default
 mechanism that transfers recovery authority from Chapter 4 to 
\series bold
Policy 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "pol:3.15"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset


\series default
(Service Continuity and Contingency Planning Policy),
 and the data and system classification framework that drives recovery prioritization during the security response phase.
\end_layout

