\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
The assigned technician (Network Administrator or Systems Administrator,
 depending on the affected system) shall create a standalone RFC record in the System of Engagement within twenty-four (24) hours of implementation,
 or by noon on the next business day,
 whichever is later.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
The IT Director shall complete catch-up CCA review within the same window.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\lang english
The assigned technician shall flag affected CI records at the time of action per 
